💋 Ruby Woo – A bold, warm-toned red that’s super bright and statement-making. Not my personal fave (a bit too warm for me), but my mom loves it and rocks it like a stunner! 👑

💋 Russian Red – Cool-toned, deeper, and more muted – totally my kind of red. Chic, classy, and flattering AF.
